Anything that does it, anything.  Basically there are two major things that are
_bad_ with ColdMUD right now (bad as in I think the server is flawed with them,
with them fixed the server would need no more mods to function, in my opinion). 
They are:

    bind()        -- it doesn't work for more than 1 port
    clear_param() -- of any syntax: we dont have it.

-Brandon/Lyncx-

(BTW, I've been rather waiting for clear_param to do a core release, and I
would like bind() so I can create a port watcher).
